# Changelog updates

After finishing any user-facing or shippable change in this repo, update `changelog.json` in the same turn before ending.

- Keep `version` aligned with `CMakeLists.txt` `project(... VERSION ...)`.
- Append concise bullets under `what_changed` describing what changed and why it matters.
- Prefer the existing style: short lead summary, then `•` bullets.
- Do not invent a new version unless the user asked to bump/release; for ongoing work on the current version, extend that entry.
- Skip trivial-only edits (typos in comments, formatting-only) unless the user asks.
